   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "70be1f8c",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Matrice de Lissage\n",
    "\n",
    "$$ S_\\lambda = B(B^TB + \\lambda I)^{-1}B^T $$\n",
    "\n",
    "$$ EDF(\\lambda) = \\mathrm{trace}(S_\\lambda) $$\n"
   ]
  },
