    "## Optimisation de λ via GCV \n",
    "\n",
    "$$ GCV(\\lambda) = \\frac{n \\sum (Y - \\hat{s}_\\lambda)^2}{(n - EDF(\\lambda))^2} $$\n"
   ]
  },
